# Code Style

## Nomenclatura
- Arquivos: kebab-case → my-component.tsx, use-auth.ts, types.ts
- Componentes React: PascalCase → export function MyComponent()
- Funcoes/variaveis: camelCase → const userName, function getUserData()
- Constantes: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE → const MAX_RETRIES = 3
- Tipos/Interfaces: PascalCase → type UserProfile, interface AuthConfig
- CSS classes: kebab-case via Tailwind utilities
- Env vars: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE com prefixo → NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, DATABASE_URL

## Estrutura de Pastas
```
src/
  app/                    # Next.js App Router (routes, layouts, pages)
    (marketing)/          # Route group: landing, pricing, about
    (app)/                # Route group: dashboard, settings
    api/                  # Route handlers
  components/
    ui/                   # Primitivos reutilizaveis (Button, Input, Card)
    layout/               # Layout components (Navbar, Footer, Sidebar)
    sections/             # Page sections (Hero, Features, Pricing)
  features/               # Feature modules (auth, billing, onboarding)
    auth/
      components/
      hooks/
      actions/
      types.ts
  lib/                    # Utilitarios compartilhados
    utils.ts              # Funcoes helper
    constants.ts          # Constantes globais
    db.ts                 # Prisma client singleton
    validations.ts        # Zod schemas compartilhados
  styles/
    globals.css           # @theme tokens + global styles
```

## Formatacao
- Indentacao: 2 espacos
- Aspas: double quotes para JSX, single quotes para JS/TS
- Semicolons: obrigatorios
- Trailing commas: obrigatorios em multiline
- Max line length: 100 caracteres (soft limit)
- Blank lines: 1 entre secoes logicas, 0 entre imports relacionados

## Componentes React
- 1 componente por arquivo
- Props type definido acima do componente
- Desestruturar props no parametro da funcao
- Retorno JSX: parenteses para multiline
- Hooks no topo do componente, antes de qualquer logica
- Event handlers com prefixo handle: handleClick, handleSubmit

## Exports
- Named exports por padrao (nao default exports)
- Excecao: page.tsx e layout.tsx exportam default (Next.js requirement)
- Re-exports via index.ts apenas em ui/ e sections/
